Still has problem, AbstractGraphicsNode.java in line 455, if clip
is not null it will call g.create(), and in line 538, if it need
offscreen buffer, then it call g.create() again, but the g.dispose()
only be called once. So, in line 534, it should be:
 if (baseG2d == null) {
  baseG2d = g2d;
  g2d = (Graphics2D)g2d.create();
 }
